CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 26, 1953, pg. 2, reads: "107th Birthday - Mrs. Sabra Washington, who was born a slave, and who celebrated her 107th birthday here Sunday with her neighbors in her home at 8141 Conemaugh Street... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Woman wearing reindeer patterned sweater, posed with arm around former slave Sabre "Mother" Washington, on Washington's 107th birthday, in her home on Conemaugh Street
